<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Moyana HR Studio</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;0,600;1,400&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root {
  --bg: #FFFFFF;
  --bg-alt: #F8F8FA;
  --bg-card: #FFFFFF;
  --ink: #0F0D0B;
  --ink-soft: #2C2A28;
  --muted: #706C68;
  --muted-light: #A8A49F;
  --border: #E6E3DD;
  --border-light: #EEECEA;
  --indigo: #3C3489;
  --indigo-mid: #534AB7;
  --indigo-light: #EEEDFE;
  --indigo-pale: #F6F5FD;
  --green-bg: #EAF2E8;
  --green-border: #C0D4BC;
  --green-text: #2A6422;
  --red-bg: #FCF0F0;
  --red-border: #EDCACA;
  --red-text: #992828;
}

* { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

body {
  font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
  background: #ECEAE5;
  color: var(--ink);
  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  font-size: 15px;
  line-height: 1.6;
}

.page {
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 920px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  background: var(--bg);
  box-shadow: 0 0 48px rgba(0,0,0,0.09);
}

/* COVER */
.cover {
  background: #FFFFFF;
  min-height: 100vh;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-rows: auto 1fr auto auto;
}

nav {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 22px 56px;
  border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--border);
}

.nav-brand {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 14px;
  font-style: italic;
  color: var(--muted);
}

.nav-badges { display: flex; gap: 7px; }

.badge {
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 400;
  color: var(--muted);
  padding: 4px 11px;
  border: 0.5px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 20px;
}

.cover-body {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  text-align: center;
  padding: 68px 56px 56px;
}

.cover-logo { width: 210px; margin-bottom: 48px; }

.cover-rule {
  width: 44px; height: 1px;
  background: var(--indigo);
  margin: 0 auto 24px;
}

.cover-eyebrow {
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: 0.2em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--indigo);
  margin-bottom: 24px;
}

.cover-headline {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: clamp(34px, 4.8vw, 58px);
  font-weight: 400;
  line-height: 1.1;
  letter-spacing: -0.025em;
  color: var(--ink);
  margin-bottom: 24px;
  max-width: 680px;
}

.cover-headline em { font-style: italic; color: var(--indigo); }

.cover-tagline {
  font-size: 15px;
  font-weight: 300;
  color: var(--muted);
  line-height: 1.8;
  max-width: 510px;
  margin-bottom: 38px;
}

.cover-tags { display: flex; gap: 8px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }

.ctag {
  font-size: 12px;
  font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  padding: 6px 15px;
  border-radius: 5px;
}

.ctag-indigo { background: var(--indigo-light); color: var(--indigo); }
.ctag-pale { background: var(--bg-alt); color: var(--muted); border: 0.5px solid var(--border); }

.cover-bottom {
  text-align: center;
  padding: 16px 56px;
  border-top: 0.5px solid var(--border);
  font-size: 12px;
  color: var(--muted);
  letter-spacing: 0.04em;
}

.cover-stripe { display: flex; height: 4px; }
.s1 { background: var(--indigo); flex: 6; }
.s2 { background: var(--indigo-mid); flex: 1; }
.s3 { background: #8880CC; flex: 1; }

/* SECTIONS */
.section {
  padding: 48px 48px;
  border-top: 0.5px solid var(--border);
  background: var(--bg);
}

.section-alt { background: var(--bg-alt); }

.section-head {
  display: flex;
  align-items: baseline;
  gap: 16px;
  margin-bottom: 22px;
}

.s-num {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 44px;
  font-weight: 400;
  color: var(--border);
  line-height: 1;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}

.s-title {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 28px;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: var(--ink);
  line-height: 1.2;
}

/* S1 PROBLEM */
.pull-quote {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 20px;
  font-weight: 400;
  font-style: italic;
  color: var(--ink-soft);
  line-height: 1.6;
  border-left: 2px solid var(--indigo);
  padding-left: 22px;
  margin-bottom: 28px;
  max-width: 620px;
  text-align: left;
}

.body-text {
  font-size: 15px;
  font-weight: 300;
  color: var(--ink-soft);
  line-height: 1.85;
  max-width: 700px;
  text-align: justify;
}

.body-text p + p { margin-top: 14px; }

.highlight-box {
  margin-top: 22px;
  background: var(--indigo);
  border-radius: 10px;
  padding: 14px 20px;
}

.highlight-box p {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 17px;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: white;
  line-height: 1.4;
  text-align: center;
}

/* S2 DO/DONT */
.duality {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 10px;
  margin-bottom: 14px;
}

.do-b, .dont-b {
  border-radius: 10px;
  padding: 16px;
}

.do-b { background: var(--green-bg); border: 0.5px solid var(--green-border); }
.dont-b { background: var(--red-bg); border: 0.5px solid var(--red-border); }

.b-label {
  font-size: 10px;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.14em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  margin-bottom: 14px;
  display: block;
}

.do-b .b-label { color: var(--green-text); }
.dont-b .b-label { color: var(--red-text); }

.b-item {
  font-size: 14px;
  line-height: 1.55;
  padding: 5px 0 5px 16px;
  border-bottom: 0.5px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
  position: relative;
  color: var(--ink-soft);
  text-align: left;
}

.b-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
.do-b .b-item::before { content: "✓"; position: absolute; left: 0; color: var(--green-text); font-size: 11px; top: 8px; }
.dont-b .b-item::before { content: "✕"; position: absolute; left: 0; color: var(--red-text); font-size: 11px; top: 8px; }

.duality-foot {
  text-align: center;
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 15px;
  font-style: italic;
  color: var(--muted);
  padding-top: 10px;
  border-top: 0.5px solid var(--border);
  margin-top: 6px;
}

/* S3 SERVICES */
.s-intro {
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 300;
  color: var(--muted);
  line-height: 1.7;
  margin-bottom: 6px;
  max-width: 580px;
}

.launch-note {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 6px;
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: var(--indigo);
  background: var(--indigo-light);
  padding: 5px 13px;
  border-radius: 5px;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
}

.svc {
  background: var(--bg-card);
  border: 0.5px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 12px;
  padding: 16px 20px;
  margin-bottom: 9px;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
  gap: 18px;
  align-items: start;
  transition: border-color 0.2s;
}

.svc:hover { border-color: var(--indigo); }

.svc-tag {
  font-size: 10px;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.14em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--indigo);
  display: block;
  margin-bottom: 6px;
}

.svc-name {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 19px;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: var(--ink);
  margin-bottom: 6px;
  line-height: 1.2;
}

.svc-desc {
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--muted);
  line-height: 1.6;
  margin-bottom: 7px;
  text-align: justify;
}

.svc-examples {
  font-size: 12px;
  color: var(--indigo-mid);
  font-style: italic;
  margin-bottom: 6px;
  line-height: 1.5;
  text-align: left;
}

.svc-chips { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 5px; }

.chip {
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--ink-soft);
  background: var(--bg-alt);
  border: 0.5px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 4px;
  padding: 3px 8px;
}

.chip-opt {
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--muted);
  background: transparent;
  border: 0.5px dashed var(--border);
  border-radius: 4px;
  padding: 3px 8px;
  font-style: italic;
}

.svc-price {
  text-align: right;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  min-width: 136px;
}

.price-val {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 21px;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--indigo);
  display: block;
  margin-bottom: 3px;
}

.price-note {
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--muted);
  display: block;
  line-height: 1.4;
}

.price-badge {
  display: inline-block;
  margin-top: 6px;
  font-size: 10px;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: var(--indigo);
  background: var(--indigo-light);
  padding: 3px 9px;
  border-radius: 10px;
}

/* Peak card */
.peak-card {
  background: var(--indigo-pale);
  border: 1.5px solid var(--indigo);
  border-radius: 12px;
  padding: 18px 20px;
  margin-top: 9px;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
  gap: 18px;
  align-items: start;
  position: relative;
}

.peak-card-label {
  position: absolute;
  top: -10px; left: 18px;
  background: var(--indigo);
  color: white;
  font-size: 9px;
  font-weight: 600;
  padding: 3px 10px;
  border-radius: 10px;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}

.peak-name {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 19px;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: var(--ink);
  margin-bottom: 8px;
  margin-top: 6px;
}

.peak-desc {
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--ink-soft);
  line-height: 1.65;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
  text-align: justify;
}

.peak-periods { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 5px; margin-bottom: 10px; }

.p-tag {
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: var(--indigo);
  background: var(--indigo-light);
  border: 0.5px solid #C8C4F0;
  border-radius: 4px;
  padding: 3px 10px;
}

.peak-sub {
  font-size: 12px;
  color: var(--muted);
  font-style: italic;
  line-height: 1.55;
  text-align: left;
}

.peak-price-area { text-align: right; flex-shrink: 0; min-width: 122px; }

.peak-price-val {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 21px;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--indigo);
  display: block;
  margin-bottom: 3px;
  margin-top: 6px;
}

.peak-price-unit {
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--muted);
  display: block;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}

.peak-limits { font-size: 11px; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.7; }

/* Coming soon */
.svc-soon {
  background: var(--bg-alt);
  border: 0.5px dashed var(--border-light);
  border-radius: 12px;
  padding: 20px 26px;
  margin-top: 11px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  gap: 16px;
  opacity: 0.7;
}

.soon-left { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px; }

.soon-badge {
  font-size: 9px;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--muted);
  background: var(--border-light);
  border: 0.5px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 4px;
  padding: 4px 10px;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  white-space: nowrap;
}

.soon-name {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 16px;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: var(--muted);
  margin-bottom: 3px;
}

.soon-desc { font-size: 12px; color: var(--muted-light); line-height: 1.5; }

.vat-line {
  text-align: center;
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--muted);
  margin-top: 18px;
  padding-top: 14px;
  border-top: 0.5px solid var(--border);
  font-style: italic;
}

/* S4 RESULTS */
.result-hero {
  background: var(--indigo-pale);
  border: 1px solid var(--indigo-light);
  border-radius: 10px;
  padding: 18px 22px;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.result-hero h3 {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 21px;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: var(--indigo);
  margin-bottom: 8px;
  text-align: left;
}

.result-hero p {
  font-size: 14px;
  font-weight: 300;
  color: var(--ink-soft);
  line-height: 1.8;
  text-align: justify;
}

.results-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 8px;
  margin-bottom: 24px;
}

.r-item {
  background: var(--bg-card);
  border: 0.5px solid var(--border);
  border-top: 2px solid var(--indigo);
  border-radius: 8px;
  padding: 12px 14px;
}

.r-icon { font-size: 16px; display: block; margin-bottom: 7px; }
.r-text { font-size: 12px; color: var(--ink-soft); line-height: 1.55; text-align: left; }

/* About */
.about-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 20px;
  align-items: start;
}

.about-title {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 20px;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: var(--ink);
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}

.about-body {
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 300;
  color: var(--ink-soft);
  line-height: 1.75;
  text-align: justify;
}

.about-body p + p { margin-top: 12px; }

.about-meta {
  margin-top: 12px;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 4px;
}

.meta-r {
  font-size: 12px;
  color: var(--muted);
  display: flex;
  gap: 7px;
  line-height: 1.55;
  text-align: left;
}

.meta-k {
  font-weight: 500;
  color: var(--ink-soft);
  flex-shrink: 0;
  min-width: 64px;
}

.contact-box {
  background: var(--bg-alt);
  border: 0.5px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 10px;
  padding: 16px;
}

.contact-title {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 17px;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: var(--ink);
  margin-bottom: 14px;
}

.c-item {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 10px;
  padding: 8px 0;
  border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--border);
  font-size: 14px;
  color: var(--ink-soft);
}

.c-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
.c-dot { width: 5px; height: 5px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--indigo); flex-shrink: 0; }

.contact-note {
  margin-top: 13px;
  padding-top: 12px;
  border-top: 0.5px solid var(--border);
  font-size: 12px;
  color: var(--muted);
  line-height: 1.65;
  font-style: italic;
  text-align: justify;
}

/* FOOTER */
footer {
  padding: 20px 56px;
  border-top: 0.5px solid var(--border);
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 10px;
  background: var(--bg);
}

.footer-brand {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 13px;
  font-style: italic;
  color: var(--muted);
}

.footer-disc {
  font-size: 10px;
  color: var(--muted-light);
  max-width: 480px;
  line-height: 1.55;
  text-align: right;
}

@media (max-width: 680px) {
  nav, .section, footer { padding-left: 22px; padding-right: 22px; }
  .cover-body { padding: 52px 22px 40px; }
  .duality, .about-grid, .results-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .svc, .peak-card { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .svc-price, .peak-price-area { text-align: left; }
  .cover-logo { width: 170px; }
}

@media print {
    * {
      -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact !important;
      print-color-adjust: exact !important;
    }
    body { background: white; }
    .page { box-shadow: none; max-width: 100%; }
    .cover { page-break-after: always; break-after: page; }
    .svc { page-break-inside: avoid; break-inside: avoid; }
    .peak-card { page-break-inside: avoid; break-inside: avoid; }
    .svc-soon { page-break-inside: avoid; break-inside: avoid; }
    .duality { page-break-inside: avoid; break-inside: avoid; }
    .highlight-box { page-break-inside: avoid; break-inside: avoid; }
    .result-hero { page-break-inside: avoid; break-inside: avoid; }
    .results-grid { page-break-inside: avoid; break-inside: avoid; }
    .r-item { page-break-inside: avoid; break-inside: avoid; }
    .about-grid { page-break-inside: avoid; break-inside: avoid; }
    .contact-box { page-break-inside: avoid; break-inside: avoid; }
    .section-head { page-break-after: avoid; break-after: avoid; }
    footer { page-break-inside: avoid; break-inside: avoid; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="page">

<!-- COVER -->
<div class="cover">
  <nav>
    <span class="nav-brand">Moyana HR Studio</span>

  </nav>

  <div class="cover-body">
    <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Moyana HR Studio" class="cover-logo">
    <div class="cover-rule"></div>
    <p class="cover-eyebrow">HR Ops Excellence Partner · EOR and Global Employment</p>

    <h1 class="cover-headline">
      Building the <em>operational back-office</em><br>
      that operational teams rarely<br>
      have time to build themselves.
    </h1>

    <p class="cover-tagline">
      Working in the background so your HR Ops teams can focus on delivering for clients and employees, without being slowed down by France's complex compliance layer.
    </p>

    <div class="cover-tags">
      <span class="ctag ctag-indigo">Back-office only</span>
      <span class="ctag ctag-indigo">EOR and Global Employment</span>
      <span class="ctag ctag-pale">France. Primary market.</span>
    </div>

    <div style="margin-top:32px;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;background:#F6F5FD;border:1px solid #EEEDFE;border-radius:6px;padding:10px 20px">
      <span style="font-size:11px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#3C3489">Launching</span>
      <span style="width:1px;height:14px;background:#C8C4F0;display:inline-block"></span>
      <span style="font-family:Playfair Display,serif;font-size:13px;font-style:italic;color:#534AB7">Moyana HR Studio · 2026</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="cover-bottom">
    melosonn.michel@gmail.com &nbsp;·&nbsp; LinkedIn: Melosonn Michel &nbsp;·&nbsp; Moyana HR Studio
  </div>

  <div class="cover-stripe">
    <div class="s1"></div>
    <div class="s2"></div>
    <div class="s3"></div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- SECTION 01 -->
<div class="section">
  <div class="section-head">
    <span class="s-num">01</span>
    <h2 class="s-title">The problem I kept seeing on the ground</h2>
  </div>

  <p class="pull-quote">
    "Every case I managed revealed the same underlying issue: the back-office HR infrastructure was incomplete, outdated, or simply missing."
  </p>

  <div class="body-text">
    <p>Having worked as an HR Ops specialist within EOR environments, primarily on the French market with additional support across EMEA, I noticed the same pattern, repeatedly.</p>
    <p>Not because teams lacked expertise. But because managing front-office delivery, responding to clients and employees in real time, leaves no bandwidth to build what should have been there from the start.</p>
    <p>Add to this the complexity of French labour law, its constant legislative changes, and the difficulty of applying them correctly in a tripartite EOR relationship. The result: avoidable escalations, documentation gaps, and overloaded HR Ops teams.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="highlight-box">
    <p>That's exactly what I work on. And why Moyana HR Studio exists.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- SECTION 02 -->
<div class="section section-alt">
  <div class="section-head">
    <span class="s-num">02</span>
    <h2 class="s-title">What I do — and what I don't</h2>
  </div>

  <div class="duality">
    <div class="do-b">
      <span class="b-label">I work on</span>
      <div class="b-item">SOP design and process mapping</div>
      <div class="b-item">Compliance frameworks. Including service provider contract verification, legal obligations review, occupational health, H&amp;S, mutual insurance, and annual leave tracking</div>
      <div class="b-item">Lifecycle documentation. Covering the full employee lifecycle from onboarding to offboarding</div>
      <div class="b-item">Client-facing education guides (FR/EN)</div>
      <div class="b-item">Legal watch and regulatory updates</div>
      <div class="b-item">Case management frameworks and decision trees</div>
    </div>
    <div class="dont-b">
